3. British Council: The official channel of the British Council offers useful tips, sample tests, and interviews with IELTS experts. <br>(<a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/britishcouncil">https://www.youtube.com/user/britishcouncil</a>)
4. E2 IELTS: Covers all sections of the IELTS test, providing valuable tips, strategies, and sample answers. <br>(<a href="https://www.youtube.com/c/E2IELTS">https://www.youtube.com/c/E2IELTS</a>)
5. IELTS Advantage: Offers in-depth lessons, techniques, and sample answers for the Reading and Writing sections. <br>(<a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/IELTSAdvantage">https://www.youtube.com/user/IELTSAdvantage</a>)

Remember to allocate time each day for focused practice and review. Stay consistent, manage your time effectively, and maintain a positive mindset. Good luck with your IELTS preparation!    
